highlights.text: “Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 608 days straight.
Roxy Dekker has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Hoe Het Is” is the highest at #2.
“No More Tears” by Ozzy Osbourne is the highest new entry on Top Songs Netherlands at #63.
“Paranoid - 2012 - Remaster” by Black Sabbath is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 136 spots at #41.
